narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I always look forward to Social Lunch; it expands my knowledge of social psych and allows me to make unexpected connections with both faculty and bodies of literature that I otherwise might not.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I enjoy being able to hear the research of other faculty, but I think we could expand our field of search to include faculty in other relevant areas such as evolutionary psychology, developmental psychology, or even philosophy, political science, or sociology.
